17
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:47,879
I…

18
00:03:50,695 --> 00:03:53,107
I didn’t think
I’d ever come back here either.

19
00:03:55,675 --> 00:04:01,305
But someone important to me
is being ordained today.

20
00:04:03,293 --> 00:04:04,705
