21
00:04:13,315 --> 00:04:14,907
Speak of the devil.

22
00:04:22,915 --> 00:04:27,405
Hard to believe it’s been almost 20 years.

23
00:05:08,854 --> 00:05:10,907
Tan, help me close the windows first.

24
00:05:10,936 --> 00:05:12,084
We can wipe it up later.

25
00:05:29,155 --> 00:05:30,905
I bet it’s a total mess outside.

26
00:05:32,130 --> 00:05:33,130
I’ll go wipe it up.

27
00:05:33,565 --> 00:05:36,082
Hey, Kongdech. Just do it later.

28
00:05:36,857 --> 00:05:38,602
We still have two whole days.

29
00:05:39,153 --> 00:05:42,602
Oh, oh, oh, so scary.

30
00:05:43,161 --> 00:05:45,429
Should I be scared?
Should I really be scared?

31
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:46,755
Hey, Father’s here.

32
00:05:48,185 --> 00:05:49,402
What’s going on?

33
00:05:49,703 --> 00:05:51,402
You boys seem to be having fun.

34
00:05:51,706 --> 00:05:53,306
Is the work done?

35
00:05:53,335 --> 00:05:55,007
Then you can finally get some rest.

36
00:05:58,307 --> 00:06:00,405
Here’s your new friend.

37
00:06:12,989 --> 00:06:14,401
Shit, the power’s out!

38
00:06:14,724 --> 00:06:15,807
Kongkit!

39
00:06:17,095 --> 00:06:18,095
Argh!

40
00:06:29,775 --> 00:06:32,035
Go tell Master Phak to check the breaker.

41
00:06:32,255 --> 00:06:33,295
- Yes, Father.
- Everyone else,

42
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:34,815
