43
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:35,839
Hurry.

44
00:06:47,407 --> 00:06:50,005
Uh… What’s your name? I’m Barth.

45
00:06:51,570 --> 00:06:52,570
Bas?

46
00:06:53,257 --> 00:06:54,257
Like basketball?

47
00:06:56,466 --> 00:06:58,795
Like the saint. Bartholomew.

48
00:06:59,715 --> 00:07:00,715
Oh.

49
00:07:00,935 --> 00:07:02,201
