57
00:07:30,536 --> 00:07:31,536
Bodin.

58
00:07:33,638 --> 00:07:34,638
Barth.

59
00:07:36,585 --> 00:07:37,602
This is Tanrak.

60
00:07:37,845 --> 00:07:39,805
He’s the head scholarship student
in Grade 12.

61
00:07:39,910 --> 00:07:43,105
He will help look after you
while you’re here.

62
00:07:45,405 --> 00:07:46,405
Yes, Father.

63
00:07:50,823 --> 00:07:54,604
You know the kids here
aren't like normal kids.

64
00:07:55,404 --> 00:07:58,345
We're here to find ourselves,

65
00:07:58,685 --> 00:08:01,558
