66
00:08:02,810 --> 00:08:03,810
Yes.

67
00:08:06,546 --> 00:08:10,103
Take your time settling in here.

68
00:08:12,065 --> 00:08:14,706
Oh, the ceremony is in just two days.

69
00:08:15,112 --> 00:08:18,402
There’s no way we’ll get
a formal uniform made in time.

70
00:08:19,045 --> 00:08:23,207
Tanrak, lend him yours for now.

71
00:08:26,250 --> 00:08:28,107
Look after our new friend, Tanrak.

72
00:08:32,027 --> 00:08:33,027
Yes, Father.

73
00:08:33,695 --> 00:08:34,695
Let’s go, Phak.

74
00:10:05,155 --> 00:10:06,155
Hey!

75
00:10:06,975 --> 00:10:09,107
Do fags really like shaving their balls?

76
00:10:09,235 --> 00:10:12,303
- What the hell?
- Hey, hey, hey.

77
00:10:13,579 --> 00:10:14,488
Let’s see. Come on.

78
00:10:14,587 --> 00:10:15,959
Hey, Kong, I’m not playing.

79
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:16,907
It’s hot.

80
00:10:16,953 --> 00:10:18,082
I’m not playing.

81
00:10:18,535 --> 00:10:20,604
- Stay still.
- Hey, let go. I’m not playing.

82
00:10:21,164 --> 00:10:22,164
Stop it.

83
00:10:22,253 --> 00:10:24,813
Plenty of nice girls out there,
but you like it from behind, huh?

84
00:10:25,008 --> 00:10:26,204
It’s hot, man.

85
00:10:26,275 --> 00:10:27,805
That’s enough!

86
00:10:28,084 --> 00:10:29,204
Hey, enough!

87
00:10:30,315 --> 00:10:31,315
The new kid’s here.

88
00:10:32,909 --> 00:10:37,755
Hey, didn’t Father say scholarship kids
