96
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:43,503
So just leave it here.

97
00:12:43,795 --> 00:12:45,607
I’ll let Master Phak know.

98
00:12:46,405 --> 00:12:47,506
Master Phak?

99
00:12:47,863 --> 00:12:52,405
