Just leave it here for now.

106
00:13:46,315 --> 00:13:47,909
I’ll let Master Phak know.

107
00:13:50,895 --> 00:13:51,895
Fine.

108
00:14:35,936 --> 00:14:37,509
And this is a formal uniform.

109
00:14:37,755 --> 00:14:39,302
We wear it for church ceremonies.

110
00:14:48,370 --> 00:14:49,370
They’re yours?

111
00:14:49,543 --> 00:14:50,543
Yeah.

112
