134
00:16:39,370 --> 00:16:40,370
Hey!

135
00:16:42,585 --> 00:16:44,079
Uh… what's your name again?

136
00:16:45,469 --> 00:16:46,500
I’m Tanrak.

137
00:16:49,035 --> 00:16:50,035
Tanrak.

138
00:16:51,660 --> 00:16:52,660
