144
00:17:17,495 --> 00:17:18,607
Barth.

145
00:17:24,385 --> 00:17:25,905
Don’t you think he’s kind of weird?

146
00:17:57,455 --> 00:17:59,655
ORDINATION MASS
DEACON VALENTINO WEERAPHAT TANGWORAPHONG

147
00:18:00,379 --> 00:18:02,407
All set. Please go inside.

148
00:18:03,164 --> 00:18:04,164
Hurry up.

149
00:18:04,361 --> 00:18:06,257
- Hey.
- Oh, Tanrak!

150
00:18:06,279 --> 00:18:07,105
Hello.

151
00:18:07,241 --> 00:18:08,505
Wow, it’s been so long.

152
00:18:08,535 --> 00:18:09,802
So good to see you.

153
00:18:09,825 --> 00:18:12,306
- I’ve missed you so much.
- Here are the aunties and uncles.

154
00:18:13,808 --> 00:18:14,905
How have you been?

155
00:18:16,863 --> 00:18:20,161
Please save me a seat up front.
I’ll follow you.

156
00:18:21,287 --> 00:18:22,408
Please save me one too.

157
00:18:23,580 --> 00:18:24,545
How have you been, Tanrak?

158
00:18:24,577 --> 00:18:27,408
I was just telling Kongdech
how much I missed you.

159
00:18:28,485 --> 00:18:30,602
Really? When did you say that?

160
00:18:30,669 --> 00:18:31,907
I didn’t hear a word.

161
00:18:32,057 --> 00:18:34,050
I was about to.

162
00:18:34,075 --> 00:18:36,705
But then we ran into Tanrak,
so I didn’t get to.

163
00:18:38,291 --> 00:18:39,605
How long ago did you arrive?

164
00:18:39,780 --> 00:18:41,205
We just got here.

165
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:44,705
Eight hours in the car. I’m exhausted.

166
00:18:44,782 --> 00:18:46,971
But Kongdech’s uncle is being ordained.

167
00:18:47,001 --> 00:18:48,404
We had to come.

168
00:18:48,635 --> 00:18:52,905
I told you to come the night before
so you wouldn’t be so tired.

169
00:18:54,396 --> 00:18:56,709
Why waste hundreds of baht on that?

170
00:18:56,735 --> 00:18:58,505
Sleeping in the car is the same thing.

171
00:18:58,965 --> 00:19:00,543
Was it comfortable, sleeping in the car?

172
00:19:00,567 --> 00:19:01,602
Come on.

173
00:19:01,635 --> 00:19:03,521
When you two get ordained,

174
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:05,470
