will definitely stay overnight.

175
00:19:05,490 --> 00:19:07,090
We might even come help set things up.

176
00:19:07,121 --> 00:19:08,121
Exactly.

177
00:19:09,075 --> 00:19:10,906
Dad, that’s over ten years away.

178
00:19:11,105 --> 00:19:13,065
You’re talking like
I’m getting ordained tomorrow.

179
00:19:13,707 --> 00:19:16,005
Time flies, doesn’t it?

180
00:19:16,128 --> 00:19:18,469
You two have known each other
since Grade 7, right?

181
00:19:18,495 --> 00:19:21,355
And just like that,
you’re almost done with Grade 12.

182
00:19:21,546 --> 00:19:22,236
That's right.

183
00:19:22,262 --> 00:19:25,706
Tanrak, I'm waiting for your ordination.

184
00:19:25,735 --> 00:19:28,605
Please look after Kongdech.
Don’t let him go off track.

185
00:19:29,903 --> 00:19:30,903
He won’t.

186
00:19:31,295 --> 00:19:33,906
We look out for each other
and study together.

187
00:19:34,774 --> 00:19:36,505
The seminary is waiting for us, buddy.

188
00:19:37,725 --> 00:19:42,081
