Should I pinch you? Should I?

192
00:19:48,482 --> 00:19:49,706
Come on, let’s go inside.

193
00:19:50,204 --> 00:19:51,302
See you later, dear.

194
00:19:52,115 --> 00:19:53,401
Listen to that mouth.

195
00:20:01,343 --> 00:20:07,604
Father in heaven, please help me…

196
00:20:09,669 --> 00:20:12,305
Tanrak, what are you doing here?

197
00:20:12,327 --> 00:20:13,705
Why haven’t you gone home?

198
00:20:14,561 --> 00:20:17,707
And why are you playing
with the incense burner like this?

199
00:20:18,174 --> 00:20:20,955
I just wanted to talk
to my mom and dad in heaven.

200
00:20:28,916 --> 00:20:30,605
Do you miss them, Tanrak?

201
00:20:33,667 --> 00:20:39,205
Your mom and dad
have just gone to heaven to be with God.

202
00:20:40,795 --> 00:20:42,401
You don’t have to feel lonely.

203
00:20:43,260 --> 00:20:47,503
They’ll always be watching over you.

204
00:20:48,047 --> 00:20:50,635
I want to be in heaven with them.

205
00:20:53,295 --> 00:20:55,202
If you're a good person,

206
00:20:56,124 --> 00:20:58,608
