and be with them?

209
00:21:09,724 --> 00:21:12,305
Do you want to come live in God’s house?

210
00:21:14,248 --> 00:21:16,303
So God can take care of you.

211
00:21:18,065 --> 00:21:22,715
And so you can wait to see
your parents in heaven again.

212
00:22:03,733 --> 00:22:07,007
Guys, have you seen the new kid?

213
00:22:07,742 --> 00:22:09,204
The ceremony’s about to start.

214
00:22:09,743 --> 00:22:11,075
I didn't see him at breakfast.

215
00:22:11,352 --> 00:22:12,903
He probably ran back home.

216
00:22:15,755 --> 00:22:17,795
It's fine. Let’s line up on standby.

217
00:22:19,786 --> 00:22:20,385
Come on.

218
00:22:20,423 --> 00:22:21,423
Hurry up.

219
00:22:22,245 --> 00:22:23,245
Hurry up, everyone.

220
00:22:26,145 --> 00:22:28,002
There he is.

221
00:22:35,045 --> 00:22:36,202
Why did you just get here?

222
00:22:37,547 --> 00:22:39,635
The ceremony starts at 9.
So I’m here at 9.

223
00:22:45,515 --> 00:22:47,346
What about the formal uniform?

224
00:22:47,365 --> 00:22:48,556
Why aren’t you wearing it?

225
00:22:56,962 --> 00:23:00,506
Go sit with the guests then.

226
00:23:15,239 --> 00:23:16,707
Everyone, line up. Hurry.

227
00:23:17,415 --> 00:23:18,415
It’s about to start.

228
00:23:21,691 --> 00:23:23,604
Brothers and sisters, please rise.

229
00:23:25,685 --> 00:23:29,903
In the name of the Father, and of the Son,
and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.

230
00:23:30,025 --> 00:23:31,025
Amen.

231
00:23:32,545 --> 00:23:36,306
Today is a very important day
for us Catholics.

232
00:23:37,235 --> 00:23:45,007
We will all witness
an ordination to the priesthood.

233
00:23:45,365 --> 00:23:46,555
Please be seated.

234
00:24:55,627 --> 00:24:57,404
Tan, shower time.

235
00:25:05,066 --> 00:25:09,103
This is the first day
of your final term in high school.

236
00:25:10,260 --> 00:25:15,407
I want all of you to study hard
and keep serving God.

237
00:25:16,435 --> 00:25:18,001
The Lord be with you.

238
00:25:18,305 --> 00:25:19,802
And with your spirit.

239
00:25:20,675 --> 00:25:27,967
May almighty God, the Father, the Son,
and the Holy Spirit, bless you all.

240
00:25:28,506 --> 00:25:30,085
- Amen.
- Amen.

241
00:25:42,085 --> 00:25:46,506
Barth, come talk to me about yesterday.

242
00:25:48,331 --> 00:25:49,331
Yes, Father.

243
00:25:50,295 --> 00:25:53,401
I know you’re angry and frustrated.

244
00:25:53,965 --> 00:25:57,505
But you shouldn’t let your heart
be consumed by anger like this.

245
00:26:00,830 --> 00:26:01,830
Yes.

246
00:26:03,857 --> 00:26:07,707
In the end, your own heart
will be the one that burns out.

247
00:26:08,475 --> 00:26:10,675
Here comes the fag.

248
00:26:10,884 --> 00:26:11,953
Hey, the fag’s here.

249
00:26:11,976 --> 00:26:12,835
Fag.

250
00:26:12,856 --> 00:26:14,503
Watch your asses, guys.

251
00:26:17,848 --> 00:26:19,404
He even walks like a fag.

252
00:26:19,712 --> 00:26:20,447
Hey, hey.

253
00:26:20,473 --> 00:26:22,506
