255
00:26:26,762 --> 00:26:27,802
A fag, huh?

256
00:26:30,386 --> 00:26:31,444
Hey, what are you gonna do?

257
00:26:31,463 --> 00:26:32,539
Hey! Hey!

258
00:26:32,559 --> 00:26:34,207
Who’s the fag now?

259
00:26:40,533 --> 00:26:43,903
I’ve never accepted any student
in the middle of the school year.

260
00:26:44,808 --> 00:26:47,002
But I believe
you’re going through a hard time.

261
00:26:47,595 --> 00:26:49,805
Maybe you prayed to God,

262
00:26:50,390 --> 00:26:54,005
